'''Absentee''', ''<code>[[noun (part of speech)|noun]]</code>''

One who absents himself from his country, office, post, or duty; especially, a [[landholder]] who lives in another country or district than that where his estate is situated; as, an Irish ''absentee''. ''[[Macaulay (source)|Macaulay]].''